Description: Nitpick programming language compiler and toolchain
 The Nitpick programming language compiler (npkc) and supporting tools.
 .
 Includes:
  - npkc: the Nitpick compiler (LLVM 20 backend)
  - npk-ls: Language Server Protocol server
  - Standard library modules
  - Package ecosystem libraries
 .
 Nitpick is a modern systems programming language with a focus on safety,
 performance, and developer experience.
